com.flyingspaniel.net.weather

Class TimeInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flyingspaniel.net.weather.TimeInterval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Ranges.Comparable<TimeInterval>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Condition, Forecast

    public class TimeInterval
extends Object
implements Ranges.Comparable<TimeInterval>
    Represents an immutable interval of time (using longs for ms since Jan 1 1970) Most methods have two forms, one taking a long (and ending in "MS"), the other a non-null Date
    Since:
    Copyright(c) 2013 Morgan Conrad
    Author:
